{"tid":1464013,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"Be Humble","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:15:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T14:31:09.000Z","uid":269585,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8a206389a0e87442e27d60493aa6d39911e6d09d","tid":1464013,"uid":269585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:15:13.000Z","msg":"大家仲記得天琦既教晦嗎？<br />\n<br />\n只要大家方向一樣我唔會割<br />\n<br />\n捉到個公安係令人激動但係要諗下<br />\n<br />\n但係我想你地諗清楚今日所做有咩值得檢討下<br />\n<br />\n輿論又會點講<br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講仲理輿論做咩<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">得民心得天下</span><br />\n<br />\n如果無民意，我地爭取既都唔係民主<br />\n<br />\n只會變成保皇黨口中既一小撮人<br />\n<br />\n大家請三思，請檢討<br />\n<br />\n我地仲有排行<br />\n<br />\n一齊行落去"},{"pid":"1a7552a9bac837c7efc88d8ca08182d37e83a97b","tid":1464013,"uid":269585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:17:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b08932ce1815134a26c948d1eca4a2936aa92b1b","tid":1464013,"uid":11515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:27:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1785aeef07dbf7a619ee303a59cbb81bcf4924e5","tid":1464013,"uid":279903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:31:09.000Z","msg":"同意：都是天琦個句，注意我們的一言一行，是否令更多人支持我們。"}]}